    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "These simple bracers look plain on the exterior, but a series of small, sharp studs line the interior like rows of shark teeth. While these bracers are worn and invested, you gain a +2 item bonus to Will saves.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
